text: America's Next Top Model, Cycle 10 is the tenth season of America's Next Top Model. This cycle includes 14 contestants. The winner was 20-year-old Whitney Thompson. ==Contestants== (In random order) * Dominique Reighard * Katarzyna Dolinska * Atalya Slater * Amis Jenkins * Aimee Wright * Marvita Washington * Whitney Thompson * Stacy-Ann Fequiere * Kimberly Rydzewski * Lauren Utter * Claire Unabia * Fatima Siad * Allison Kuehn * Anya Rozova ==Prizes== * A modeling contract with Elite Model Management * A spread in Seventeen Magazines * A $100,000 contract with CoverGirl * A new wardrobe design by a designer of your choice * A new mansion in Hollywood * A free trip around the world ==Episodes== 1\. casting episode 2\. *Quit: Kimberly Rydzewski *Best: Anya Rozova *Worst: Atalya Slater & Amis Jenkins *Eliminated: Atalya Slater 3\. *Best: Lauren Utter *Worst: Allison Kuehn & Dominique Reighard *Eliminated: Allison Kuehn 4\. *Best: Anya Rozova *Worst: Fatima Siad & Amis Jenkins *Eliminated: Amis Jenkins 5\. *Best: Stacy-Ann Fequiere *Worst: Whitney Thompson & Mavita Washington *Eliminated: Marvita Washington 6\. *Best: Whitney Thompson *Worst: Claire Unabia & Aimee Wright *Eliminated: Aimee Wright 7\. *Best: Fatima Siad *Worst: Claire Unabia & Lauren Utter *Eliminated: Claire Unabia 8\. *Best: Anya Rozova *Worst: Stacy-Ann Fequiere & Fatima Siad *Eliminated: Stacy-Ann Fequiere 9\. *Best: Fatima Siad *Worst: Lauren Utter & Whitney Thompson *Eliminated: Lauren Utter 10\. *Best: Fatima Siad *Worst: Katarzyna Dolinska & Whitney Thompson *Eliminated: Katarzyna Dolinska 11\. *Best: Anya Rozova *Worst: Fatima Siad & Dominique Reighard *Eliminated: Dominique Reighard 12\. *Best: Anya Rozova *Worst: Fatima Siad & Whitney Thompson *Eliminated: Fatima Siad *Final Two: Anya Rozova & Whitney Thompson *Winner: Whitney Thompson Category:America's Next Top Model
